{
  "stem": "19441.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they steal a-- a tomato.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They put it in her-- they've been so flat, you didn't see it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If they'd been lucky that nobody looked through, so she went through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But if they found it, you went to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So someone was risking their life to bring you--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're risking their life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They bring the tomato.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And with that, I rubbed my tongue, so-- you know, because it soothe it a little bit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, the same thing was I wanted [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] lemonade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A girl was working in the SS canteen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She again on her-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like she risked her life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she-- she steal a bottle of lemonade and she brought it to me, so that's what I was living.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg pardon?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was from our-- our town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if she was Helen or-- can't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were so many names, can't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I know she did that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, it was that-- it was the danger that the SS man by the name [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shtibitz. ?] He was a big sadist, and he couldn't-- couldn't quicker and quicker get the people to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and we couldn't walk and couldn't get up, we've been so weak.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we stayed in bed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So but--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "30 girls was-- all had typhoid and they all was in bed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we thought that during day, nobody will come in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in any case, some girls who was close to me, whom I helped all the time-- that's how it is, one helps the other.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said to one of the girls who-- who was also from our group, you do the night shift for Magda and she will say that she's night shift.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
